{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"6okho30ws0l6sxu9we8i8bv","title":"Kubectl","desc":"","updated":1666361556653,"created":1666272326629,"custom":{},"fname":"dev.ops.kubernetes.kubectl","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"26faa0cbdf397b91db7d2771d93455b4","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"x8fgptqq97o6wh9z5yfbu6n","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"kubectl\">Kubectl<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kubectl\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Node 확인</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ kubectl get <span class=\"token function\">node</span> -o wide\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Pod 생성 및 실행</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">-- 하나만\n$ kubectl run nginx-pod --image<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ngnix\n\n-- 여러 개\n$ kubectl create deployment dpy-nginx1 --image<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>nginx\n$ kubectl run my-first-nginx --image<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>nginx --replicas<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Pod 확인</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ kubectl get pods\n$ kubectl get pods -o wide\n$ kubectl get deployment\n$ kubectl get pod,deploy\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Yaml 파일 실행</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ kubectl create -f dpy-nginx2.yaml\n$ kubectl apply -f dpy-nginx.yaml\n$ kubectl edit deploy dpy-nginx2\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Pod 삭제</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ kubectl delete pod --all\n$ kubectl delete deployment --all\n$ kubectl delete svc --all\n$ kubectl delete deployment,pod,svc --all\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>모니터링</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">$ <span class=\"token function\">watch</span> kubectl get pods -o wide\n</code></pre>","noteIndex":{